Citation.sTitle: Solubility of D(-)-p-Hydroxyphenylglycine Dane Salt in Eight Alcohols between (293 and 343) K
Citation.sAbstract: The solubility of D(-)-p-hydroxyphenylglycine dane salt (HPGDane Salt) in eight alcohols was measured using a laser technique with the temperature range from (293 to 343) K. The results were correlated with a semiempirical equation, the calculated results of which are proved to show fine representation of experimental data.
